id: pm-github-urs1
title: Route GitHub export dry-run preview to stderr so stdout stays valid JSON
description: "pm github export --format json corrupted stdout: extension console.log'd the preview to stdout while the SDK host also renders the return object to stdout, yielding JSON+trailing-YAML. Fix: route the md/JSON preview to stderr like the existing [dry-run] note. Non-breaking; --format json to raw stdout never worked. Mirror of companion item pm-cli-website-ex9n."
